    <h2>Apostle's Creed</h2>
    
    <p>I believe in God, the Father almighty,<p>
creator of heaven and earth.<p>

I believe in Jesus Christ, God's only Son, our Lord,<p>
who was conceived by the Holy Spirit,<p>
born of the Virgin Mary,<p>
suffered under Pontius Pilate,<p>
was crucified, died, and was buried;<p>
he descended to the dead.<p>
On the third day he rose again;<p>
he ascended into heaven,<p>
he is seated at the right hand of the Father,<p>
and he will come to judge the living and the dead.<p>

I believe in the Holy Spirit,<p>
the holy catholic Church,<p>
the communion of saints,<p>
the forgiveness of sins,<p>
the resurrection of the body,<p>
and the life everlasting. Amen</p>
</div>
